{"title":"炎州旅怀","authors":["潘昌鸿"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":3,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"炎州旅怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾　潘昌鸿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十余年念故乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盈盈弱水感苍茫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"间关万里家书到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是伤心即断肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年辞母夜登程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾尽私藏壮旅行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更有几多心上语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔村犹听唤儿声。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}